{"tid":1036374,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《英雄聯盟》俄羅斯女子戰隊遭5 Ban輔助 官方判ROX性別歧視","createTime":"2019-02-25T07:42:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T14:55:55.000Z","uid":185134,"like":45,"dislike":270,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"2ed8b5317cb3d1c9e22a08fadddcb2562627646c","tid":1036374,"uid":185134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T07:42:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3905/d3905515.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3905%2Fd3905515.jpg&h=ee15e49d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記者周之鼎／台北報導<br />\n<br />\n日前我們曾報導「俄羅斯《英雄聯盟》女子戰隊遭5Ban輔助血虐 引爆性別大戰」，而「英雄聯盟歐陸聯賽（LCL）」主辦方，同時也是遊戲開發商的Riot Games在今（2/22）日發出懲處公告，認為ROX顯然有歧視女子戰隊Vaevictis Esports之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n事件的起因是ROX對上Vaevictis Esports的比賽中，在賽前的選禁角首搶輔助，再陸續Ban了五個輔助角色，通常全力封鎖一個位置是為了針對某位選手的戰術，但事實上兩隊本來就有一些實力差距，所以其實不見得得用到這種戰術，這也讓一些觀眾與官方認為ROX是看不起 Vaevictis 所做的挑釁行為，藉以諷刺對手只會玩輔助。另一件事則是Vega Squadron同樣對上Vaevictis Esports的比賽，Vega Squadron在比賽中早早就取得巨大優勢，但顯然並不想結束遊戲，在比賽中上演一場超級虐殺秀，這場比賽最終人頭數是以52:2的超懸殊差距結束。這場比賽也讓Vega Squadron同樣遭到官方懲處。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QVuleUiQ6nk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQVuleUiQ6nk&d=g2%2Fo6b0QjPi1xWtu1PcU8RR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=9b4db7f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QVuleUiQ6nk</a><br />\n▲ROX 5Ban輔助。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/l2pC52I-vwE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fl2pC52I-vwE&d=g2%2Fo6b0QjPi1xWtu1PcU8RR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=649fbb57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/l2pC52I-vwE</a><br />\n▲Vega Squadron上演52:2超級虐殺秀。<br />\n<br />\n官方在公告中認為，ROX在對上Vaevictis的比賽中，禁用了5名輔助角色雖然技術上並不違反規則，但這是對俄羅斯女子隊Vaevictis Esports不尊重且帶有性別歧視的表現。Riot Games認為性別歧視是在職業比賽場上完全不能被接受的行為。ROX和Vega Squadron的惡劣行為違反了LCL的規定，以及召喚師守則第9條，向ROX和Vega Squadron戰隊發出警告，如果再發生違規行為，他們將會有更加嚴厲的處罰。公告中並且希望LCL的所有選手都能表現出競爭誠信並尊重他們的對手。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://game.ettoday.net/article/1384527.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgame.ettoday.net%2Farticle%2F1384527.htm&d=g2%2Fo6b0QjPi1xWtu1PcU8RR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=75d0e1f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://game.ettoday.net/article/1384527.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n5ban sup都唔得 惡撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22daa0666ecb04a374a144600e074fd538907de5","tid":1036374,"uid":154725,"like":161,"dislike":77,"score":84,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T07:51:38.000Z","msg":"雖然個sup pool咁撚淺係廢<br />\n<br />\n但好撚無品 寧願ban人地main英 或者戰術角好過啦"},{"pid":"c884f70e8a1c6e55e64a793adf7f4a25313fa8c4","tid":1036374,"uid":73054,"like":325,"dislike":1,"score":324,"quote":{"pid":"22daa0666ecb04a374a144600e074fd538907de5","tid":1036374,"uid":154725,"like":161,"dislike":77,"score":84,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T07:51:38.000Z","msg":"雖然個sup pool咁撚淺係廢<br />\n<br />\n但好撚無品 寧願ban人地main英 或者戰術角好過啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T07:57:52.000Z","msg":"人地咪Main sup"},{"pid":"d8ec0e984afb7775f498f30882256f2a4fb1bc1d","tid":1036374,"uid":202051,"like":230,"dislike":2,"score":228,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T08:13:13.000Z","msg":"咁樣係串而且冇品嘅但唔覺關性別歧視事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a7b9291e22f5de1482f05af34c7e1bef9c9e2fe","tid":1036374,"uid":197857,"like":141,"dislike":13,"score":128,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T08:37:19.000Z","msg":"亂ban都係唔尊重架啦<br />\n但虐殺show先係最仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a55cb28cbeeef0467838614192f172ec1b8a591a","tid":1036374,"uid":55375,"like":103,"dislike":0,"score":103,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T08:48:11.000Z","msg":"咩叫亂ban串<br />\n入面5條友有4個main sup 1個副sup"},{"pid":"186d985f985dddc3d36ab01befbd7e6fb7297b5c","tid":1036374,"uid":197857,"like":269,"dislike":0,"score":269,"quote":{"pid":"3a7b9291e22f5de1482f05af34c7e1bef9c9e2fe","tid":1036374,"uid":197857,"like":141,"dislike":13,"score":128,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T08:37:19.000Z","